================================================ *\/\n    @media screen and (max-width: 650px) {\n\n        body {\n            background-color: #ffffff !important;\n        }\n\n        \/* Membalik urutan susunan Header (Logo di atas, teks di bawah) *\/\n        .header-table {\n            display: table !important;\n            width: 100% !important;\n        }\n\n        .header-table tr {\n            display: table !important;\n            width: 100% !important;\n        }\n\n        .header-table .header-logo {\n            display: table-header-group !important;\n            width: 100% !important;\n            text-align: left !important;\n            padding-bottom: 8px !important;\n            \/* Jarak dari logo ke elemen di bawahnya *\/\n        }\n\n        .header-table .header-title {\n            display: table-footer-group !important;\n            width: 100% !important;\n            text-align: left !important;\n            font-size: 20px !important;\n            \/* Mengecilkan font jadi 20px *\/\n            padding-top: 18px !important;\n            \/* Memberikan padding top 18px *\/\n        }\n\n        .header-table .header-logo img {\n            margin: 0 !important;\n        }\n\n        \/* --- Perbaikan Info Table Agar Tidak Terpotong di Mobile --- *\/\n        .info-table .label {\n            width: 135px !important;\n            \/* Mempersempit kolom label agar sisa kolom kanan luas *\/\n            white-space: normal !important;\n            font-size: 14px !important;\n        }\n\n        .info-table .colon {\n            width: 15px !important;\n        }\n\n        .info-table .value {\n            font-size: 14px !important;\n            word-break: break-word;\n            \/* Teks variabel panjang otomatis patah baris dengan aman *\/\n        }\n    }\n\n    \/* ==========================================================================\n    Responsive Queries (Dark Mode Global - Dipisah, Tidak Boleh Bersarang)\n   ========================================================================== *\/\n    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {\n        body {\n            background-color: #2a2d33 !important;\n        }\n\n        .logo-white {\n            display: block !important;\n        }\n\n        .pre-code {\n            background-color: #727272 !important;\n            border-color: #727272 !important;\n        }\n\n        .border-color {\n            border-left: 1px solid #5a5a5a !important;\n            border-right: 1px solid #5a5a5a !important;\n        }\n\n        .border-color-2 {\n            border-left: 1px solid #5a5a5a !important;\n            border-right: 1px solid #5a5a5a !important;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #5a5a5a !important;\n        }\n\n        .hr {\n            margin: 0 !important;\n            padding: 0 !important;\n            border: 1px solid #e7e8e8 !important;\n        }\n\n        .text-company,\n        .font-heading,\n        .font-body {\n            color: #fff !important;\n        }\n    }\n    <\/style>\n<\/head>\n\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n    <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"header-table\">\n        <tr>\n            <td class=\"header-title\" style=\"\n                font-size: 28px;\n                font-weight: bold;\n                color: #ffffff;\n                vertical-align: middle;\n            \">\n                Portal Disbursement\n            <\/td>\n            <td class=\"header-logo\" align=\"right\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\">\n                <img src=\"http:\/\/wp-disbursement.localhost\/assets\/img\/img-logo-jatelindo.png\" alt=\"Logo Jatelindo\" style=\"display: block; height: 35px; width: auto\" \/>\n            <\/td>\n        <\/tr>\n    <\/table>\n<\/div>        <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n    <tr>\n        <td class=\"content-cell\">\n            <h2>Halo, <strong>Checker MBG<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n            <p>Silakan gunakan kode OTP berikut untuk melanjutkan proses perubahan password. Demi keamanan, jangan\n                bagikan kode kepada siapa pun.<\/p>\n            <p>Kode OTP berlaku selama 15 menit.<\/p>\n\n            <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n                <tr>\n                    <td style=\"padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 16px;\">\n                        <div class=\"pre-code\">\n                            <pre style=\"margin: 0\">665537<\/pre>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/td>\n                <\/tr>\n            <\/table>\n\n            <p style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\n                Terima kasih,<br>\n                <strong>Portal Disbursement<\/strong>\n            <\/p>\n\n            <hr>\n\n            <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #555555; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n                Apabila membutuhkan bantuan atau informasi lebih lanjut, silakan hubungi kami melalui kontak berikut\n                ini:<br>\n                <strong>Email :<\/strong> support@portal-disbursement.co.id<br>\n                <strong>Phone :<\/strong> 081234567890\n            <\/p>\n        <\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n<\/table>        <div class=\"footer\">\n    PT Jatelindo Perkasa Abadi<br \/>\n    Jalan Sunan Kalijaga Blok K5 No.63B, Melawai, Kebayoran Baru, Jakarta\n    Selatan 12160\n<\/div>    <\/div>\n<\/body>\n\n<\/html>","isHtml":true} HEADER={"X-API-KEY":"07575ebb-fb9d-11f0-997f-00163e012243","Content-Type":"application\/json","Authorization":"*****","X-SIGNATURE":"4e73ccb61709a0b3b777954655fc90b094e67afd932f2d1eafd93554f15f8615"}
